Actinver Acquires Majority Stake in Pure Leasing

-- B y   J o n a t h a n   R o e d e r
-- 
2011-05-06T20:31:42Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-06/actinver-acquires-majority-stake-in-pure-leasing-correct-.html
(Corrects Pure Leasing’s line of business in story
published yesterday.)  Corp. Actinver SAB, a Mexican
brokerage and provider of financial services, acquired 51
percent of the shares of Pure Leasing SA, according to a
statement to  Mexico ’s stock exchange.  Pure Leasing, a lessor of equipment and goods, has total
assets of 1.5 billion pesos, Actinver said. It did not disclose
financial terms of the deal.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Jonathan Roeder in Mexico City at 
 jroeder@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Jonathan Roeder at 
 jroeder@bloomberg.net  